Package: stratosync
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libfuse3-3, fuse3, rclone
Recommends: python3-nautilus
Suggests: python3-nemo, python3-caja
Description: Linux cloud sync daemon with on-demand FUSE3 filesystem
 Stratosync provides a FUSE3 virtual filesystem backed by rclone, supporting
 70+ cloud storage providers. Files appear immediately with metadata-only
 placeholders, hydrate on open(), and uploads propagate automatically with
 conflict detection and 3-way merge resolution.

Package: stratosync-dolphin-overlay
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, stratosync (= ${binary:Version})
Enhances: dolphin
Description: Sync-status emblem overlays for Dolphin and Konqueror
 KOverlayIconPlugin (KF6) that adds sync-status emblem overlays in Dolphin
 and Konqueror, matching the Nautilus / Nemo / Caja Python extensions.
 Pulls in KF6 KIO at runtime — install only on KDE Plasma desktops.
